palette_data.reasoning: This palette combines warm and cool hues to evoke expressive emotion. The bold coral (#FF6F61) energizes and creates warmth, while the muted purple (#6B5B95) introduces depth and introspection. The fresh green (#88B04B) adds vitality, balanced by the soft pink (#F7CAC9) for gentleness. The calm blue (#92A8D1) brings harmony and visual stability, resulting in a balanced yet emotionally dynamic composition.
